<plot>The School the story of Edgar, a grade school teacher, who attempts to demonstrate the wonder life to his class through nature studies and other class projects. Despite his best intentions, each of the projects go badly and comically wrong. At a loss to explain why, Edgar is faced with a class who attempt to grapple with the larger implications of these failures.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?588820</url></doc>
